snippet.textDisplay: having aged twelve years and played all the others, i still have the opinion that red and blue had the most heart and soul put into it.  silver was good.  i loved ruby.  fire red and platninum are great, too.  but this... transcends all of them.  not because of game mechanics, but because of the music, the sprites, and the story.  no end of the world crap (r/s/e/d/pr/pl), you're just trying to be the best, while saving animals from evil bastards and putting them in boxes.  oh, the irony.
